     *     <li>URL Encoding enabled/disabled</li>
     *     <li>Config</li>
     *     <li>Proxy Specification</li>
     *     <li>Content-Type allowed/disallowed</li>
     * </ul>
     * The following settings are merged:
     * <ul>
     *     <li>Parameters</li>
     *     <li>Query Parameters</li>
